  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Studying in a RCT the changes in everyday llife activities of children with CP during
      HABIT-ILE or control period, changes being scored by parents and by experts.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Studying in a RCT the changes in everyday llife activities of children with CP (unilateral
      and bilateral) during HABIT-ILE or control period, changes being scored by parents and by
      experts on ABILHAND-Kids, the PEDI, the ACTIVLM-CP and the COPM. Investigate neuroplastic
      changes and correlation with everyday life changes.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
