  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  cerebral palsy

          -  ability to make a few steps with a walking device

          -  ability to pick a light object from a table with the more affected hand

          -  ability to understand simple games

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  no active seizure

          -  no botulinum toxin in the 6 months previous to the intervention or during intervention
             time

          -  major visual deficit
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
